quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  108,1,“Ndithu takupatsa zabwino zambiri (zina mwa izo ndi mtsinje wotchedwa Kauthar)
  108,2,"“(Pakuti ndakupatsa zimenezo), pitiriza kupembedza Mbuye wako (moyera mtima) ndipo ipha nsembe yako (chifukwa chakuthokoza Allah pa zimene wakupatsa, monga ulemelero ndikukusankhira zabwino zambiri)"
  108,3,“Ndithu mdani wako ndiye ali wopanda mwawi